1.0.0.name: wordpress/photo-book
1.0.0.description: Photo Book  is a cool responsive WordPress theme for building online portfolios, gallery websites or image based blogs. The theme is great setting up an online galleri of your work, if you are designer, artist, photographer, or other creative specialist. The theme supports widgets and custom menus.
